PROJECT EmailAgent
INTENT Classify incoming emails and draft a response only when confidence is high.
MODE classification
ENTITY Email

FIELDS Email
  urgency
  sender_trust
  topic_support
  topic_sales
  sentiment
  has_attachment
  previous_interactions
  language_confidence
END

GOAL classify_incoming_email
GOAL minimize_false_replies

CONSTRAINT confidence > 0.95
ACTION_THRESHOLD 0.90

ACTION DraftReply
  POLICY simulate_only
  CALL simulated.email.draft
END
